The '''Tourism Grading Council of South Africa''' is an independent assessment agency that attempts to establish a common set of standards ([[Star (classification)|"star ratings"]]) by which patrons of [[hotel]]s, [[guest house (lodging)|guest house]]s, [[conference venue]]s, and other accommodation facilities may compare different establishments.

